Paper: hep-th/9705119

Date: 1997-05-15

Title: Virasoro Algebra and O(N) Sigma Model

Authors: Jiannis Pachos (MIT)

Comments: 13 pages, REVTEX, no figures

Journal-ref: Int.J.Mod.Phys. A14 (1999) 25-40

Within the framework of a local expansion of the logarithm of the O(N)sigma-model vacuum functional, valid for slowly varying fields, the modifiedVirasoro algebra is studied. The operator-like central charge term is given, upto second order, for a general functional.